text: Patrik Marcel (born November 27, 1994) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Přerov of the Czech Extraliga. Marcel made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Plzeň during the 2013–14 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:HC Plzeň players Category:Czech ice hockey defencemen
